parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected stalling of the engine can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities, especially when occurring at high speeds.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning
often while driving at high speeds
and may not restart immediately. The vehicle may experience a sudden loss of power
and the driver may be unable to maintain control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause catastrophic engine damage, leading to costly repairs and potentially stranding the vehicle owner. In some cases, this failure can occur without warning, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The timing chain breaks
causing engine damage
and potentially leading to costly repairs. The vehicle may experience loud popping noises
and the engine may fail to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective throttle body can cause the engine to stall without warning, leading to loss of control and potentially serious accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning
often while driving at high speeds
and may not restart immediately. The vehicle may experience a sudden loss of power
and the driver may be unable to maintain control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall while driving, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission makes a growling noise
the vehicle is hesitant when accelerating
the transmission does not shift gears correctly
the vehicle will not go into drive from reverse
the vehicle stops suddenly while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery drain can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery runs down quickly
the vehicle will not start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear vision mirror can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially in low-light or inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: The rear vision mirror fogs up
the rear vision mirror leaks an oily substance
the rear vision mirror becomes cloudy or opaque
the rear vision mirror is unable to provide a clear view.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wipers can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially in rainy or snowy conditions.
symptoms: The windshield wipers suddenly stop working
the windshield wipers fail to clear the windshield
the windshield wipers make a loud noise or vibrate excessively
the windshield wiper arm becomes loose or detached.
